        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '1516'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 40,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: '???', 3: '...This technology can simulate human growth at the highest level.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'A large cylindrical capsule opens. The gray-haired girl\\'s eyes are closed as she lies still in translucent fluid.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Laid down next to her is an identical humanoid body. A cable connects the two of them, and shimmering blue lights goes back and forth along the cable.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 43,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Behind a thick glass wall, several humans in suits are observing the process.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 44,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'A human in a white lab coat stands in the front, vivaciously describing his ideas.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 45,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500138'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 46,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Male Researcher', 3: '...Unlike machines, our organic bodies never stop changing.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 47,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Male Researcher', 3: 'Humans consume food to gain nutrients, which are transformed into our muscles and bones. The temporary supplements for them are, in turn, excreted as waste every single day.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 48,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Male Researcher', 3: '\"Humans are vortexes in the river of life.\" The information we carry is always refreshing and renewing.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 49,
        "ActionId": 49,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Male Researcher', 3: 'How is our information created, cataloged, stored, and updated? Are these systems applicable to machines?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 50,
        "ActionId": 50,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Male Researcher', 3: 'If \"feelings\" are not simply \"byproducts of neural activities,\" then perhaps \"emotions\" are something mechanical lives can look forward to one day.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 51,
        "ActionId": 51,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 203,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '0.25', 3: '400'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 52,
        "ActionId": 52,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '500340', 4: '-400'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 53,
        "ActionId": 53,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Person In Suit', 3: '...We don\\'t care about that.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 54,
        "ActionId": 54,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Person In Suit', 3: 'Even if machines possess these \"emotions\" you mentioned, we can\\'t treat them as being alive.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 55,
        "ActionId": 55,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Person In Suit', 3: 'Machines are tools at the end of the day, aren\\'t they?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 56,
        "ActionId": 56,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Person In Suit', 3: 'Can you guarantee that this phenomenon is under control? Once machines possess \"free will\"... Don\\'t forget that the machine consciousness experiment was launched to negate that risk.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 57,
        "ActionId": 57,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Person In Suit', 3: 'We are preparing for the future.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 58,
        "ActionId": 58,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Male Researcher', 3: 'If the essence of the universe is information, then the codes in computer programs can also be considered a form of life.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 59,
        "ActionId": 59,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Male Researcher', 3: 'Isn\\'t that one of the reasons why the Science Council named their Super AI \"Gestalt\"?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 60,
        "ActionId": 60,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Male Researcher', 3: 'If we only try to control instead of understanding them, humankind will certainly be destroyed by their own hubris.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 61,
        "ActionId": 61,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Person In Suit', 3: 'You...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 62,
        "ActionId": 62,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
